                    <li>Unicast, broadcast, multicast frames</li>
                    <li>Collision domains vs broadcast domains</li>
                  </ul>
                </td>
                <td><span class="level-pill int">Intermediate</span></td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><span class="module-label">4.3 Basic switch configuration</span></td>
                <td>
                  <ul class="topic-list">
                    <li>Accessing switch: console, remote login (overview)</li>
                    <li>Hostname, passwords, banner</li>
                    <li>Assigning management IP to VLAN 1</li>
                  </ul>
                </td>
                <td><span class="level-pill int">Intermediate</span></td>
              </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </article>

